item.title: CVE-2024-0156|2024-03-04T12:55:23.100Z -- Dell -- Dell Digital Delivery (D3)
item.description: Dell Digital Delivery, versions prior to 5.0.86.0, contain a Buffer Overflow vulnerability. A local low privileged attacker could potentially exploit this vulnerability, leading to arbitrary code execution and/or privilege escalation.
